title: Thursday Post Show (02-17-22)

description:
Bobby talks about cancel culture and addresses issues on when it’s okay to like someone again. Also how the Tindler Swindler now has a Hollywood Agent. We also take a look at Throwback Thursday. We take some callers who have questions for Eddie about Suzy Bogguss and him wanting to find time to work out.
